ygData.subject: Leveling for Human Druid @ 9
ygData.msgSnippet: Hello, Everyone was so helpful for the lvl 20, could some one help me. I am a human druid lvl 9 and am wondering where to go, without getting my buns
ygData.messageBody:
Hello,<br>Everyone was so helpful for the lvl 20,
could some one help me. I am a human druid lvl 9 and am
wondering where to go, without getting my buns toasted.
Currently I am in the Kaladim area and am soloing. Right
now no-one wants to group or lvl with me, which is
okay, I am still new and my magic isn't that powerful
yet. Where in Norath or on the moon may I go to have
some fun and adventure without getting killed every 5
minutes?<br>Appreciate in advance all the help I can get.<br>Cat
